Castle of Chillon has stood over Lake Geneva since Middle Ages. ; Photo, 
Trophies and suits of armor are among artifacts on display in the restored 
castle at Montreux. ; Photo, Lush grounds surround castle made famous in Lord 
Byron verse. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
